{
  "experiment": "D3_GBM_stage3 -- Prospective Blind Drug Prediction in GBM (Stage 3)",
  "stage": 3,
  "stage_description": "First genuinely prospective blind prediction in the IRDME cancer drug discovery pipeline. Prior experiments (D3_v1, D3_v2, D3_CRC_v1, D3_PDAC_v1) were retrospective against existing PRISM data. In this experiment, we (1) build the GBM network, (2) run the perturbation loop to get delta-r values, (3) commit this prediction file, and ONLY THEN (4) open PRISM glioma LFC data and test. The delta-r values were computed without accessing any PRISM LFC data for glioma lines.",
