  "nodes_excluded_from_prism_test": {
    "CDK4": "Cytostatic class — CDK4/6 inhibitors (palbociclib/ribociclib/abemaciclib) arrest cells in G1 but do not kill; PRISM LFC is inadequate readout. Established in D3_PDAC_v1.",
    "MYC": "BET inhibitor potency gap — JQ1/OTX015 suppress MYC ~70% but residual MYC is sufficient for survival. Confirmed D3_v1 (LFC=-0.128) and D3_v2 (LFC=+0.240, cells GROW).",
    "MDM2": "TP53-WT gating — nutlin-3/AMG-232 only effective in TP53-WT cells. GBM is ~30% TP53-mutant in primary GBM, so unselected glioma lines are mixed TP53 status. Cannot test without TP53-WT stratification.",
